OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FSpoiler warning: This article reveals
OL,7,Fthe winner of the I'm A Celeb show
OL,9,FAdam Thomas has been crowned the
OL,10,Fwinner of I'm A Celebrity... South
OL,11,FAfrica, earning the title of "ultimate
OL,12,Flegend 2026", after the live final
OL,13,Fshow descended into chaos.
OL,15,FThe 37-year-old actor was voted the
OL,16,Fwinner by public vote during the live
OL,17,Ffinal on Friday, with fellow finalists
OL,18,FSir Mo Farah in second place and Harry
OL,19,FRedknapp in third.
OL,26,@sD@^OUtD@LO]
