OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777136757
OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FDuring the final, the former Waterloo
OL,7,FRoad star was accused of being
OL,8,F"abusive, aggressive and intimidating"
OL,9,Fby former footballer Jimmy Bullard.
OL,11,FThe episode became chaotic after David
OL,12,FHaye joined in the conversation to
OL,13,Faccuse the show of editing footage to
OL,14,Fmake Thomas look like a "victim" and,
OL,15,Fafter defending the actor, Sinitta and
OL,16,FGemma Collins walked off set.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@fO]vD@YOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
