OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777136757
OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FThomas has hit headlines since
OL,7,Fappearing on the all-star show for his
OL,8,Ffeud with boxer Haye, who he said
OL,9,F"broke" him and pushed him to his
OL,10,Flimits, and for his row with campmate
OL,11,FBullard for almost compromising his
OL,12,Ftime on the show.
OL,14,FBullard discussed their explosive row
OL,15,Fon the show, claiming Thomas dropped
OL,16,F"c-bombs" which were not aired, and
OL,17,Fasked hosts Anthony McPartlin and
OL,18,FDeclan Donnelly for their opinion as
OL,19,Fthey had "front row seats".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@GO]xD@AOUxD@IO]{D@JOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777136757
OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FMcPartlin disagreed that the exchange
OL,7,Fwas aggressive and said: "No it
OL,8,Fwasn't, I was there."
OL,10,FThomas responded by saying he took
OL,11,F"full responsibility" for his actions
OL,12,Fand he has "nothing but love for
OL,13,FJimmy", but Haye interrupted the
OL,14,Fexchange and said: "You've got a funny
OL,15,Fway of showing it."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@UO]sD@AOUsD@UO]tD@LOUuD@FO]vD@
OL,26,ATOUwD@SO]
