PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777136757
OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FThe interaction spiralled into chaos
OL,7,Fafter the boxer was then asked about
OL,8,Fsome of his controversial comments on
OL,9,Fthe show, and he said: "I like to say
OL,10,Fit like I see it," and accused the
OL,11,Fshow of editing footage in favour of
OL,12,FThomas.
OL,14,FHe added: "We all had banter back and
OL,15,Fforth, and a lot of it was cut out
OL,16,Ffrom their side."
OL,18,FHaye and Bullard then asked their
OL,19,Ffellow contestants to agree Thomas had
OL,20,Fbeen "abusive, intimidating and
OL,21,Faggressive" in his row with Bullard.
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@RO]vD@KOUxD@QO]|D@FOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
