PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777136757
OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Sinitta and Collins
OL,7,Fdefended the actor but eventually
OL,8,Fwalked off set, with the former The
OL,9,FOnly Way Is Essex star commenting that
OL,10,FHaye was "aggressive".
OL,12,FThe dramatic episode later saw Thomas
OL,13,Fcrowned the winner by reality TV star
OL,14,FSam Thompson, who won the original
OL,15,Fseries in 2023, and said being on the
OL,16,Fshow was a "blast".
OL,18,FReflecting on his time in the jungle,
OL,19,FRedknapp, who came third, said he "met
OL,20,Flots of nice people and really enjoyed
OL,21,Fit".
OL,26,@rD@JOUrD@UO]xD@LOUxD@RO]{D@cOU}D@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
