OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FSir Mo hailed the experience as
OL,7,F"amazing" and "entertaining", and said
OL,8,Fhe feels like he has made his family
OL,9,Fproud.
OL,11,FCraig Charles was awarded fourth place
OL,12,Fduring the episode, which saw the
OL,13,Ffinalists face insects, reptiles and
OL,14,Fother creepy crawlies in a series of
OL,15,Fpre-recorded trials filmed last autumn
OL,16,Fas they each fought to earn stars for
OL,17,Ftheir final jungle banquet.
