OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHaye interrupted the episode early on
OL,12,Fas he questioned whether Thomas
OL,13,Fdeserved to win due to his interaction
OL,14,Fwith Bullard, after Collins hailed him
OL,15,Fas her "hero" and rooted for him to
OL,16,Fwin.
