OL,3,CI'm A Celebrity's second all star
OL,4,Cseries crowns 'jungle legend'
OL,6,FMcPartlin joked that the "scariest
OL,7,Fthing" the celebrities have faced this
OL,8,Fseries were "David Haye's views about
OL,9,Fwomen", referencing the boxer's
OL,10,Fremarks on "ugly birds" while
OL,11,Fdiscussing his girlfriend Sian Osborne
OL,12,Fwhich left viewers in uproar.
OL,14,FAnt and Dec also offered "support and
OL,15,Flove" to soap star Beverley Callard,
OL,16,Fwho was unable to attend the live
OL,17,Fevent.
